precis:
Amendment to SCHEDULE A to the FOOD AND DRUG ACT Schedule No. 832 removing
the diseases of pneumonia, poliomyelitis, tetanus and tuberculosis from
Schedule "A" so that vaccine prophylaxis or treatments can be advertised
to the general public.
